                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 6775/236.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">President of Salvador</gloss> to
                        President <persName type="to">Roosevelt</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">San Salvador</hi>
                        </placeName>,<lb/>(Received <date calendar="gregorian" when="1907-11-19"
                            >November 19, 1907</date>.)</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>I have the honor to inform Your Excellency that peace and tranquillity having
                    been restored throughout the country, the constitutional path was entered this
                    day, the state of siege raised, and absolute and unconditional amnesty granted
                    to cover all political offenses.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">F. Figueroa.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
